sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Suspicious Execution From GUID Like Folder Names
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects potential suspicious execution of a GUID like folder name located in a suspicious location such as %TEMP% as seen being used in IcedID attacks
Detects unusual processes accessing desktop.ini, which can be leveraged to alter how Explorer displays a folder's content (i.e. renaming files) without changing them on disk.
